{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Shadowhand Solitaire is a <strong>casual, solitaire-only</strong> edition of Shadowhand: RPG Card Game with no turn-based combat. Gameplay is similar to other hit games in the series: Regency Solitaire &amp; Regency Solitaire II. </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199380/extras/RIDE_WITH_SHADOWHAND_HEADER.png?t=1739805219\" />Follow the story of Lady Cornelia Darkmoor, a beguiling young aristocrat who masquerades as the notorious highwaywoman, Shadowhand.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Fleeing a crime scene and forced to act under the cover of darkness, Shadowhand's mission to safeguard a woman she holds dear leads to a web of corruption, smuggling and blackmail.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199380/extras/CharacterTabsFrame600.png?t=1739805219\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199380/extras/SET_IN_18TH_C_ENGLAND_HEADER.png?t=1739805219\" />Shadowhand's historical visual novel narrative spans 22 chapters of atmospheric locations including stormy coastlines, mysterious woods and gloomy manors. Featuring over 150 levels of elegant and intense single-player card action, dodge the law and brawl with outlaws in this swashbuckling adventure.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199380/extras/CharacterTabsFrame600.png?t=1739805219\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199380/extras/STAND_AND_DELIVER_HEADER.png?t=1739805219\" />Your fortune and freedom are at stake! Customize your character to unlock gameplay features, and become the ultimate highwaywoman! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199380/extras/CharacterTabsFrame600.png?t=1739805219\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199380/extras/Features_Header.png?t=1739805219\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">    Smooth, satisfying solitaire gameplay.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">    Disguise Lady Cornelia in spectacular costumes.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">    Sumptuous art and dramatic adventure story.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">    Prequel to Regency Solitaire (in 1770s England)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">    Over 150 unique levels spread over 22 chapters </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">    Unlock dozens of exciting gameplay upgrades.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">    Relaxed, Normal and Hard modes. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">    Specially-composed, classical music.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">    Set backgrounds as Desktop Wallpaper.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199380/extras/CardFan_modifiedforSS.png?t=1739805219\" /></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Liberty & Justice For All","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3199380/79c78eb14e07d7d8cd688a5ee77ec501732d4ebf.jpg"},{"name":"Hardcore Outlaw","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3199380/276b95c2d1a26519782701416630c9684375ced9.jpg"},{"name":"Relaxed Ruffian","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3199380/a29222dbe5902a6d7c4b1d847de7117dcd05f233.jpg"},{"name":"Perfectionist","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3199380/ca09b5b158206075e780aeb6748458f5caeb32bc.jpg"},{"name":"Star Quality","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/